markets.title: Will the Department of Justice sue an AAU university for failing to comply with Students For Fair Admission v Harvard this year?
markets.rules_primary: If the Department of Justice has initiated a legal complaint, action, or lawsuit against a university that is a member of the Association of American Universities alleging violations of the Supreme Court’s ruling in Students for Fair Admission v. Harvard before Dec 31, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
